column5: Hi Just like to introduce myself to everyone here and thank you all for the knowledge I have gained from this site. I am a retired electrician with a passion for fishing and classic high performance cars. Counting the days to get back in the boat and out onto the water again.  Cheers glenn
Welcome to the site Glenn!
Welcome to the board !!!!!!!!!!!!!
Welcome Home .. Glenn!   Randy
Welcome Glenn, any car pic's to share??  Thanks for the intro,  MTBF
Welcome aboard Glenn. Looking forward to hearing of your adventures.
hello bonjour!
So all we know about you so far Glen is that you stutter !  Classic cars.. fishing.. we could probably get along! lol  Welcome aboard, where you from?

Hi MTBF Always willing to share pics of the kids.  The blue coupe is a 65 350 H.P. Silver 62 340 H.P. 83 Mercedes 65 Shelby Cobra 400+H.P Z28 Camero (camera shy)  Hope this works as I had to reduce the pics.  Cheers glenn
